Package: mutenm
Type: Package
Title: Mutate Elastic Network Models of Proteins
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Julian Echave
Maintainer: Julian Echave <jechave@unsam.edu.ar>
Description: Build elastic network models (ENMs) of proteins and calculate
    mutation-response matrices using the linear-force ENM (LFENM) perturbation
    model. Provides tools for analyzing how mutations propagate structural
    effects through proteins.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10),
Imports:
    pracma,
    bio3d,
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    stats,
    tibble,
    tidyr
